01:15:43.623 --> 01:15:45.333
(Whirring)

01:15:48.461 --> 01:15:49.921
(Squelching)

01:15:50.046 --> 01:15:51.464
Aow!

01:15:51.589 --> 01:15:53.508
Just had to be sure...

01:15:58.638 --> 01:16:00.807
