01:20:02.173 --> 01:20:06.093
Ice cream man, it's all in his head.

01:20:08.012 --> 01:20:10.014
Ah!

01:20:15.394 --> 01:20:17.647
It's time now, boy.

01:20:19.106 --> 01:20:21.400
Yes...

01:20:21.484 --> 01:20:23.194
