01:21:08.322 --> 01:21:09.991
Mike!

01:21:47.695 --> 01:21:48.946
(Groaning)

01:22:02.001 --> 01:22:04.045
(Ghostly groaning)

01:22:20.394 --> 01:22:21.979
No.

01:22:47.672 --> 01:22:49.966
(Squelching)

01:22:50.049 --> 01:22:52.301
Ah! Ah!

01:22:52.385 --> 01:22:54.929
