01:23:45.229 --> 01:23:47.064
(Mike groans)

01:23:47.148 --> 01:23:49.400
Mike? Mike?

01:23:49.483 --> 01:23:51.110
You're still alive.

01:23:53.362 --> 01:23:55.031
